{"tid":2443731,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港台：本港二手樓價於春節假期後上升","createTime":"2021-03-12T08:40:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-12T08:54:42.000Z","uid":290404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b425bf50e9a341e95d4fdf64cded28cb876c502f","tid":2443731,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T08:40:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n反映本港二手樓價走勢的中原城市領先指數最新報178.89，創29個星期新高，指數按星期升近1%，創9個星期最大升幅。連同大型屋苑指數同中小型單位指數，3大指數連續3星期上升，是去年5月後首次，累計都升約1.6%。<br />\n<br />\n至於大型單位指數按星期升2.33%，是9個星期以來最大升幅。<br />\n<br />\n按地區劃分，新界東樓價指數按星期跌1.05%，其餘3區都上升。<br />\n<br />\n今日公布的指數有近80%交易在上月中至21日簽訂臨時買賣合約，反映農曆新年假期後首個星期市況。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1580272-20210312.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1580272-20210312.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=RGPktlJYpqjIeXpZRAkgw2vf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=b1101e88\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1580272-20210312.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=a7a0c3ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1580272-20210312.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"ad92b9783c549162e79014e277d26a494e313284","tid":2443731,"uid":184103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T08:45:28.000Z","msg":"好嬲好嬲"},{"pid":"9a31093fa9d82d6d266345592b7f00dcaadb8b3f","tid":2443731,"uid":19287,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T08:49:15.000Z","msg":"有新台長唔出奇"},{"pid":"00eb6628f4e9202377f9f6645937d0ec43366a55","tid":2443731,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T08:50:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fc5e8949b289745454195ea19820f0d63916053","tid":2443731,"uid":375847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0